                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180506-70-off389 t18180506-70-crimeloc392"></join>. On the 19th of January I let the prisoner a furnished room at 5s. 6d. a week-the articles stated in the indictment were let with the lodging. On the 13th of February I missed her. I got the door forced open, and missed the things, which I found at the office. On the 16th of April my husband brought her home - She told us where she had pledged the property.</p>
